casebody.data:
D. A. Ewing, et al., Plaintiffs in Error, v. D. G. Gordon, Defendant in Error. T. F. West, for Plaintiff in Error; J. W. Kehoe and Laird & McGeachey, for Defendant in Error.

Writ of error to judgment of Circuit Court for Santa Rosa County.

Writ of error dismissed on motion of counsel for Defendant in error.
